  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oil in a wok over medium heat.",
    "Add oxtail and cook until golden brown, about 5 minutes.",
    "In a small bowl, mix soy sauce and vinegar. Pour into the wok with ginger and shallots.",
    "Stir-fry for another 3-4 minutes or until the sauce thickens slightly.",
    "Season with black pepper to taste.",
    "Add green onions on top before serving."
